<plot>The Bible and the Book of Mormon both claim to be ancient, historical texts, and God-breathed scripture. But can any of these claims be put to the test? This documentary places both volumes to archaeological, historical, and textual scrutiny in order to determine which can legitimately be called authentic historical texts...and more to the point, which can even be in the running for "the Word of God".</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?543442</url></doc>
